SUMMARY:Beyond the Net Grant Program
DESCRIPTION:The Internet Society Foundation’s Beyond the Net Grant Program offers fu
 nding to support Internet Society Chapters to implement innovative proje
 cts that make a local impact by providing meaningful access to an open\,
  trusted\, and globally-connected Internet\, as well as strengthening th
 e Chapters’ presence in the surrounding community.
URL:https://www.isocfoundation.org/grant-programme/beyond-the-net-grant-program/
