UID:90890b72-94b7-508c-ad7f-3db364d1a113
SUMMARY:Research Grant Program
DESCRIPTION:The Internet Society Foundation’s Research Program supports global resea
 rch collaborations that advance understanding of the Internet and its va
 lue for all. Furthering our 2030 strategic objectives\, the program fost
 ers ideas and innovation that further the long-term goal of a world wher
 e people everywhere enjoy affordable\, reliable\, resilient Internet acc
 ess and a safe\, secure\, and trustworthy online experience.
URL:https://www.isocfoundation.org/grant-programme/research-grant-programme/
DTSTAMP:20240101T000000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260522
